item.title: HackTheBox - Devel Writeup
item.author: SH∆FIQ ∆IM∆N
item.description: Enumeration scan top 1000 ports 1 nmap -sC -sV -oN nmap/initial 10.10.10.5 the result nmap initial scan all ports scan 1 nmap -sC -sV -p- -oN nmap/all_ports 10.10.10.5 the result nmap allports scan Open Ports We all know both Nmap scan shows us, just 2 open ports 21/FTP = Microsoft ftpd 80/HTTP = Microsoft IIS httpd 7.5 FTP File Transfer Protocol [FTP] on this machine is open and allowed login as anonymous Let’s connect to it ftp anonymous Well, I can’t find anything on it So, I’m thinking this FTP might have been connected to the other port [port 80].
